ime":"2019-05-24T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"3c668f1765dd35833be9d217802a7aa6ed485cfa","tid":1169789,"uid":255216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T20:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee46f0f6f3f5f9915636d90cd6f3a0f2af0998e","tid":1169789,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T20:22:45.000Z","msg":"有返當年反國教，學民思潮招人自發搞街站種氣氛"},{"pid":"c5d08a5aee21fb93cdec8ae49e706a2d23795fa4","tid":1169789,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T20:46:47.000Z","msg":"在訪問期間，Alvin說得頭頭是道，一點都不是鬧著玩，包括修訂後法庭把關的說法、剔走九項經濟罪行等，他均曾深入了解，「香港同中國係兩個法制嚟，點可以引渡呢？你話我聽。」<br />\n<br />\n巴打好波呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77777fb79b34a63388e4bf9e78976d840b7b1de","tid":1169789,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f54295f75080b98fc884f48b0159d647637ee7","tid":1169789,"uid":103513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"哩班人已經好過連登一半人，唔係得個鍵盤<br />\n<br />\n連登仔唔想再畀人笑鍵盤戰士今次就應該要企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8191553483603cff621df3d38f66e2c5ccba2a96","tid":1169789,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}